        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "接下来你必须选择一个视频格式，它描述了连接到你的帧抓取器的相机和要获取的图像 的 大 小 。 视 频 格 式 被 指 定 为 字 符 串 ， 并 且 必 须 是 FrameGrabber 对 象 的AvailableVideoFormats方法返回的字符串之一。这个示例代码声明了一个视频格式:const string VIDEO_FORMAT "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "="
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "\"Sony XC75 640x480\";"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                179,
                112,
                847,
                181
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "content": {
                "title_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "四、 Create an Acquisition FIFO"
                    }
                ],
                "level": 1
            },
            "bbox": [
                146,
                187,
                410,
                200
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "要创建一个新的获取 FIFO，需要使用 FrameGrabber 对象的 CreateAcqFifo 方法，传递要使用的视频格式和 CogAcqFifoPixelFormatConstants。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                179,
                205,
                847,
                237
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "使用 Sony XC-75 相机创建一个适用于获取宽 640 像素、高 480 像素的灰度图像的FIFO采集，并采用默认的FIFO像素格式:"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                179,
                241,
                847,
                275
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "code",
            "content": {
                "code_caption": [],
                "code_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "ICogAcqFof myFifo = null; "
                    }
                ],
                "code_language": "txt"
            },
            "bbox": [
                181,
                279,
                371,
                293
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "algorithm",
            "content": {
                "algorithm_caption": [],
                "algorithm_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "myFifo  "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "\\equiv"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": " myFrameGrabber.CreateAcqFifo(VIDEOFormats,CogAcqFifoPixelFormatConstants.F ormat8Grey,0,false); "
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                181,
                297,
                843,
                330
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "一旦创建了一个获取FIFO，就可以修改诸如亮度和对比度之类的属性。您可以在任何时候更改获取FIFO属性。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                179,
                334,
                847,
                368
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "content": {
                "title_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "五、 Acquire an Image"
                    }
                ],
                "level": 1
            },
            "bbox": [
                146,
                390,
                347,
                406
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "一个 ICogAcqFifo 对象有两种方法可以用来开始获取图像:"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                181,
                407,
                630,
                424
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "ICogImage Acqire(out int triggerNumber) "
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                299,
                435,
                699,
                454
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "int StartAcquire() "
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                300,
                472,
                465,
                491
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "使用Acquire将获取请求放置到队列中。如果没有其他请求挂起，则立即进行取像。否则，获取请求将保留在队列中，直到能够处理为止。下面的编程语句使用Acquire方法返回对 CogImage8Grey 对象的引用。CogImage8Grey 类表示一个 8 位的灰度图像。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                169,
                500,
                847,
                556
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "CogImage8Grey myImage; "
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                171,
                575,
                389,
                590
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "int trigNum; "
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                173,
                594,
                268,
                608
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "code",
            "content": {
                "code_caption": [],
                "code_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "myImage = (CogImage8Grey)myFifo.Acquire(out trigNum); "
                    }
                ],
                "code_language": "javascript"
            },
            "bbox": [
                173,
                612,
                636,
                627
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "FIFO队列的大小被限制为32个请求，必须获取图像才能从FIFO队列中删除它们。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                169,
                649,
                813,
                665
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "如果不这样做，FIFO将被填充，随后的图像将无法获得。您可以使用"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                171,
                668,
                715,
                683
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "CompleteAcquire来获取未取像完成的图像，或者使用Flush来删除未完成的请求。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                171,
                686,
                813,
                702
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "使用GetFifoState来监视FIFO中挂起的获取请求的数量。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                171,
                705,
                620,
                720
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "调用StartAcquire方法将启动新的取像，而不等待当前取像完成。然后必须将返回值传递给 CompleteAcquire 方法以获得图像。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                169,
                741,
                847,
                776
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "注：Acqire(）方法会将取像请求放置在取像队列中，按顺序完成；而StartAcquire()"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                171,
                806,
                843,
                824
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "方法不会等待，直接取像，然后需要调用CompleteAcquire()方法获得图像。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                171,
                843,
                847,
                860
            ]
        }
